Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.00,0:00:08.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome to the Velvet Room.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.75,0:00:13.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Only those who are bound by a contract may enter here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.36,0:00:17.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have awakened to your power most brilliantly.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.01,0:00:20.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please take this with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.57,0:00:25.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is the Contractor's Key.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.15,0:00:30.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From this night forth, you are our guest in the Velvet Room.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.75,0:00:33.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your Persona ability is that of the wild card.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.50,0:00:37.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Compared to that of others, it is very special.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.06,0:00:41.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is like the number zero: Empty, yet holding infinite potential within itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.73,0:00:48.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I look forward to traveling the road of your destiny together
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.79,0:00:51.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to see where your awakened power of the wild card will take you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{OP sky's the limit}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.07,0:01:07.15,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}Glaciers of ideas, importing
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.15,0:01:08.36,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}To my friends, then exporting
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.36,0:01:09.87,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}To the next, keeping it open
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.87,0:01:10.78,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}We want no closing
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.78,0:01:12.87,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}Even without those, our thoughts can be duped
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.87,0:01:14.37,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}This mind trade no one can stop
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.37,0:01:16.41,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}An act of thinking is terrible to stop
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.41,0:01:18.08,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}We just wanna change it up, not drop
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.08,0:01:20.08,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}And my crew can rock it like uprock{APPARENTLY A REAL THING: http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Uprock}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.08,0:01:22.04,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}Life is tedious if it ain't flowing
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.04,0:01:23.96,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}Copy and paste? Constant defaulting?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.96,0:01:24.76,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}Put my courage to it
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.76,0:01:25.59,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}Begin showing off
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.59,0:01:26.72,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}That's the way we wanna live
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.72,0:01:27.67,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}Keep going, yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.67,0:01:31.01,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}What was so much of transparency
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.01,0:01:35.64,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}Turned into bright expectation
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.64,0:01:42.40,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}Instinct tells me to keep going together, going together
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.40,0:01:49.03,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}It's breathtaking moments in life
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.03,0:01:56.54,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}Addicted to it, minds craving more and more
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.54,0:02:01.33,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}I'm believing you and I can do anything
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.33,0:02:05.25,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}We can change the world
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.75,0:02:09.34,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}The sky's the limit, we can spread wings
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.34,0:02:16.01,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,200)}to roadless travel, together we go
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.34,0:02:47.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Satonaka!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.01,0:02:50.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Satonaka! Wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.49,0:02:54.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Satonaka!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.87,0:02:55.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.49,0:03:00.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where'd the monsters go?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.14,0:03:01.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're gone for good.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.76,0:03:02.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gone?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.91,0:03:04.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's the one who killed them!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.12,0:03:05.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.50,0:03:07.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was seriously amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.61,0:03:11.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard you call it... "Persona," was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.03,0:03:15.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really know.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.54,0:03:20.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's just get out of here before more of those things come.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.02,0:03:20.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.79,0:03:23.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd love to, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.52,0:03:24.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.83,0:03:28.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An exit?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.81,0:03:30.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We finally found you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.30,0:03:32.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You seem like you know this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.73,0:03:35.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First, tell me what happened to the Shadows!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.61,0:03:37.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean those monsters back there?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.73,0:03:38.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.74,0:03:39.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, right!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.74,0:03:41.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you provoke them?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.70,0:03:44.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bear-ish the thought!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.24,0:03:48.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've had it up to here with people barging in here and riling up the Shadows!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.00,0:03:53.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,TVs?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.21,0:03:56.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now off with you! Beat it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.95,0:03:59.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a busy bear!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.83,0:04:01.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.68,0:04:02.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey now!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.72,0:04:03.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take it easy!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.78,0:04:11.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.54,0:04:12.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn that bear.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.06,0:04:15.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're back?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.90,0:04:17.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank God!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.65,0:04:19.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We made it!{I'm glad to be alive!}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.33,0:04:23.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't take advantage of the situation!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.14,0:04:28.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.10,0:04:31.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the same poster I saw over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.66,0:04:33.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right. It's Hiiragi Misuzu.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.55,0:04:37.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's been on the news a lot lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.82,0:04:42.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Her husband's the one who had the affair with the announcer that died.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.33,0:04:44.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wait a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.09,0:04:47.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, now. What about that freaky room?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.41,0:04:51.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She may be connected to the death of Ms. Yamano.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.92,0:04:53.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't go there!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.63,0:04:55.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think my heart can take it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.88,0:04:58.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh shit, I forgot! I gotta go to the bathroom!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.93,0:05:01.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is giving me the chills.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.33,0:05:04.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't feel so good. I gotta go.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.02,0:05:16.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I went through hell yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.40,0:05:17.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.64,0:05:21.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll tell you some other time, but you probably won't believe me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.79,0:05:24.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you're Yukiko, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.20,0:05:30.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been waiting for a while now, Yukiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.26,0:05:32.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.49,0:05:36.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's hang out and have some fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.07,0:05:37.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.73,0:05:39.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it! You're scaring her!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.19,0:05:41.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, Yukiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.62,0:05:42.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where'd he come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.23,0:05:45.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Amagi challenge ain't that easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.42,0:05:48.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, are you coming or not?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.33,0:05:51.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not going.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.27,0:05:54.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine then!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.66,0:05:55.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn bitch.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.81,0:05:59.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yo!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.93,0:06:00.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.85,0:06:02.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.35,0:06:03.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.05,0:06:05.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did he want?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.71,0:06:08.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was obviously asking you out on a date!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.45,0:06:10.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.70,0:06:12.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You couldn't tell?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.84,0:06:15.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so cruel, Amagi!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.81,0:06:18.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You did the same thing to me last year.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.30,0:06:19.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.51,0:06:21.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't remember that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.29,0:06:23.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wanna go out then?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.68,0:06:25.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'd rather not.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.02,0:06:25.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.80,0:06:28.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.88,0:06:31.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My heart already belongs to someone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.51,0:06:32.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Konishi, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.08,0:06:34.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.24,0:06:39.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Although, she hasn't texted me back since yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.80,0:06:41.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.07,0:06:44.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, man...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.46,0:06:45.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did something happen again?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.60,0:06:50.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, where's Amagi?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.53,0:06:53.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She left after her family called her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.89,0:06:56.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They needed her help at the inn.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.50,0:06:57.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What inn?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.05,0:07:02.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Her family owns the nicest traditional inn in town.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.82,0:07:05.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And Yukiko is the heir.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.57,0:07:09.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's up with her?{senpai=Konishi}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.53,0:07:11.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She still hasn't responded.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.98,0:07:13.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.87,0:07:17.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The principal has something to say, so pay attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.74,0:07:21.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Talking out of turn will earn you a spot on my shit list!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.84,0:07:22.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So pipe down!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.72,0:07:29.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I regret to inform you that I have a terrible announcement to make.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.17,0:07:34.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Konishi Saki of Class 3-B was found dead early this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.77,0:07:36.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.88,0:07:39.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please remain calm.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.31,0:07:45.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been assured by the faculty that she wasn't the victim of bullying.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.59,0:07:50.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Her body was hung like Ms. Yamano's.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.25,0:07:53.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it was a telephone pole this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.97,0:07:58.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hanamura...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.55,0:08:05.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, did you guys watch the Midnight Channel last night?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.03,0:08:08.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You wanna talk about that now?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.75,0:08:10.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just hear me out!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.97,0:08:16.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something was bothering me, so I watched it last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.96,0:08:20.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I think I saw Konishi on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.82,0:08:23.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.20,0:08:30.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One of our classmates saw Ms. Yamano on the Midnight Channel and claimed she was his soul mate.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.25,0:08:31.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I remember that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.78,0:08:37.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I heard that Konishi vanished before her death, just like Ms. Yamano.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.03,0:08:39.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That can't be a coincidence.{Could that :really: be a coincidence?}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.76,0:08:41.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.26,0:08:46.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think people who show up on TV die?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.35,0:08:50.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Remember how we saw a poster of Hiiragi Misuzu over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.46,0:08:55.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You think the TV world is connected to the murders?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.59,0:09:00.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Konishi and Ms. Yamano may have gone in there at some point!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.79,0:09:04.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hanamura, don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.43,0:09:07.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously, don't do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.90,0:09:09.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We were able to come back once, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.92,0:09:14.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we go in from the same location, maybe we'll meet that bear again.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.63,0:09:17.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Maybe" isn't good enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.15,0:09:20.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I'll go with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.98,0:09:23.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.08,0:09:25.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I could really use your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.18,0:09:28.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Satonaka, I'm leaving you in charge of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.92,0:09:32.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! Are you being serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.30,0:09:34.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.39,0:09:37.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, are you ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.48,0:09:38.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.58,0:09:43.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Wait, I tell you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.25,0:09:58.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.49,0:10:01.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This was never gonna work!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.31,0:10:02.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now what?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.30,0:10:12.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn, that hurt!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.76,0:10:15.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, it's you two again!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.34,0:10:17.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You came back?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.80,0:10:19.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the same place after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.94,0:10:21.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You two are bear-y suspicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.98,0:10:22.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.92,0:10:28.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lately, I can tell someone's been throwing people in here before the fog lifts.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.07,0:10:29.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The fog?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.16,0:10:32.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know that if it's foggy on your side, the fog lifts here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.86,0:10:38.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I do recall it being foggy on the days Ms. Yamano and Konishi died.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.57,0:10:41.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think anyone forced you in here,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.94,0:10:44.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so you must be the one's throwing people in!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.87,0:10:47.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You two are the culprits!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.44,0:10:49.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've gotta be kidding!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.81,0:10:50.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's crazy!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.82,0:10:51.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.93,0:10:58.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that Konishi and Ms. Yamano were thrown into this world?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.42,0:11:02.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Obviously, you guys did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.38,0:11:03.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just admit it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.68,0:11:08.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? How do we know {\i1}you{\i0} didn't do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.56,0:11:13.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take off that stupid costume and show us your face!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.15,0:11:13.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.94,0:11:15.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take it off!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.78,0:11:19.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What the hell?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.40,0:11:23.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.80,0:11:27.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's empty! What's up with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.98,0:11:31.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you bear-y much.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.45,0:11:33.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Narukami, does {\i1}anything{\i0} faze you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.87,0:11:34.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.14,0:11:39.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I'll believe that you guys aren't the culprits.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.01,0:11:40.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was quick.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.56,0:11:44.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I want you to find the real guy who did all this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.94,0:11:46.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have to stop him!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.99,0:11:49.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The culprit?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.10,0:11:53.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just want to live here in peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.33,0:11:55.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this thing for real?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.21,0:11:59.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the only ones who can do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.11,0:12:00.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you promise?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.23,0:12:03.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do we have to?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.54,0:12:04.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.18,0:12:05.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.16,0:12:07.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way! You're going along with it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.85,0:12:10.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I feel sorry for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.87,0:12:12.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.47,0:12:15.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're being way too nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.99,0:12:17.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.66,0:12:20.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You better help us out then, stupid bear.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.30,0:12:25.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! I can see so clearly with these on!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.42,0:12:28.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, this looks like the shopping district.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.75,0:12:31.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I last saw a girl over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.29,0:12:32.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you dumb bear.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.14,0:12:34.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this the girl you're talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.40,0:12:36.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's her all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.95,0:12:40.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She disappeared into that store.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.88,0:12:42.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's her family's place.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.47,0:12:44.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you hear that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.91,0:12:48.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I wish Junes would go under.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.07,0:12:51.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Oh, I heard that Konishi's daughter is working there.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.87,0:12:55.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}How could she, with her family's business suffering like it is?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.50,0:12:56.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What a troublesome child.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.73,0:12:59.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's that talking?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.21,0:13:00.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut the hell up!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.67,0:13:01.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hanamura!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.31,0:13:05.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Saki, how many times do I have to tell you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.05,0:13:10.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}As the eldest daughter of the {Konishi }family who owns this liquor store, aren't you ashamed of yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.26,0:13:13.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}How dare you get a part-time job at Junes?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.06,0:13:15.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that her dad's voice?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.89,0:13:18.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why can we hear this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.00,0:13:19.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, is someone there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.57,0:13:25.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.84,0:13:28.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the ticket I gave her.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.36,0:13:30.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I never had the chance to say it...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.20,0:13:32.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Konishi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.39,0:13:34.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Is that you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.62,0:13:36.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please! Where are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.73,0:13:39.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I always wanted to tell Hana...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.11,0:13:41.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.53,0:13:44.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...that he was a real pain in the ass.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.26,0:13:50.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I was only nice to him because he was the store manager's son.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.71,0:13:54.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But he takes it completely the wrong way and gets all enthusiastic.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.96,0:13:55.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pain in the ass?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.15,0:13:59.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Who cares about Junes, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.76,0:14:02.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The liquor store, the shopping district, my parents...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.65,0:14:05.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I wish everything would just disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.11,0:14:09.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're lying! This can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.26,0:14:11.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way she's like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.87,0:14:17.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.10,0:14:20.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel so sorry for myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.14,0:14:25.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, {\i1}I'm{\i0} the one who thinks everything's a pain in the ass!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.72,0:14:33.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that right, "me"?
