Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.71,0:14:50.98,Default,,0000,0000,0100,,Oh, my. Oh, my.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.98,0:14:52.28,Default,,0000,0000,0100,,There are two Yosukes?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.47,0:14:55.48,Default,,0000,0000,0100,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.48,0:14:56.97,Default,,0000,0000,0100,,I'm you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.33,0:14:59.16,Default,,0000,0000,0100,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.16,0:15:02.02,Default,,0000,0000,0100,,I know everything about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.03,0:15:06.52,Default,,0000,0000,0100,,And coming here for Konishi's sake?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.52,0:15:08.74,Default,,0000,0000,0100,,What a load of shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.74,0:15:13.16,Default,,0000,0000,0100,,You just came because you thought it sounded like a good time!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.16,0:15:16.81,Default,,0000,0000,0100,,What else is there to do out in this shithole?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.68,0:15:19.98,Default,,0000,0000,0100,,That's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.47,0:15:24.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If all went well, hey, maybe you could even be a hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.23,0:15:28.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And your sweetheart's death was the perfect excuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.34,0:15:32.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.61,0:15:33.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.61,0:15:36.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am a Shadow...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.89,0:15:38.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The true self...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.16,0:15:40.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am {\i1}your{\i0} Shadow.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.41,0:15:44.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fuck that! I don't know you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.32,0:15:49.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! Say it again!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.66,0:15:53.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.47,0:15:59.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that's right. I'm me now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.59,0:16:02.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not you anymore, see?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.06,0:16:07.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That Shadow's getting bigger!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{TS sign: Burning up!}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.95,0:16:17.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Persona!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.78,0:16:26.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay, Hanamura?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.87,0:16:28.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're amazing, Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.19,0:16:31.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You really hit it hard!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.98,0:16:33.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.96,0:16:37.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's nothing like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.64,0:16:41.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That thing came from you, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.49,0:16:42.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bullshit!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.68,0:16:48.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You put on a good show of being carefree and happy-go-lucky...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.64,0:16:51.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,'cause you're so terrified of being alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.39,0:16:52.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.78,0:16:55.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not me! I don't know you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.67,0:17:09.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's attracting nearby Shadows!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.79,0:17:14.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Master, if we don't stop it soon, this'll get grizzly!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.09,0:17:23.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know everything about you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.43,0:17:27.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know how pathetic you really are!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.10,0:17:31.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Let's ask Hanamura to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.61,0:17:33.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The prince of Junes?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.60,0:17:37.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He thinks everyone depends on him because he's the manager's son.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.10,0:17:39.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What a loser!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.72,0:17:42.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You knew you were a nuisance,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.64,0:17:46.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but you played the part of the good guy well!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.63,0:17:48.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut the hell up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.50,0:17:50.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here it comes!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.45,0:17:57.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Booyah!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.59,0:18:02.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He takes it completely the wrong way and gets all enthusiastic.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.91,0:18:06.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You asked her out 'cause you're sick of living in the boonies!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.54,0:18:08.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You just wanted to do something fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.21,0:18:11.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.02,0:18:11.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.98,0:18:15.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're wrong, wrong, wrong, wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.70,0:18:14.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now disappear!{shadow yosuke}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.46,0:18:16.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Izanagi!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.37,0:18:20.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.41,0:18:21.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oops. Wrong guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.22,0:18:24.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What gives?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.32,0:18:25.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You loved her, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.69,0:18:27.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Konishi, that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.56,0:18:29.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.06,0:18:31.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I truly loved her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.89,0:18:33.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then isn't that enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.16,0:18:40.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.94,0:18:42.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She dumped ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.60,0:18:43.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.18,0:18:47.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it wasn't lying,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.79,0:18:50.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I was so ashamed that I didn't want to admit.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.03,0:18:53.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To get along with others,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.75,0:18:56.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had to change the way I acted.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.01,0:18:58.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even I think I'm annoying.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.76,0:19:03.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But my feelings for her were real.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.29,0:19:08.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That thing's a part of me, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.53,0:19:12.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When you get down to it, all of this is me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.44,0:19:18.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! Shut up, you brat!{if I hear one more uzzee I'm going to kill someone}{lol}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.27,0:19:21.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There! Now's your chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.57,0:19:24.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Izanagi!{TS sign: Burning up!}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.55,0:19:49.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're me...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.65,0:19:51.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I'm you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.06,0:20:08.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So this is my...{yos}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.03,0:20:10.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Persona.{yu}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.62,0:20:15.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Narukami.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.26,0:20:18.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You really saved my ass.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.17,0:20:20.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, dude.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.37,0:20:30.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.26,0:20:31.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That hurt...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.97,0:20:35.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys came back!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.26,0:20:37.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.37,0:20:40.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.01,0:20:44.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The rope got cut off, and I had no idea what to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.85,0:20:47.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The nerve of you guys! You're such morons!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.58,0:20:50.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe this! You guys suck!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.61,0:20:51.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Satonaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.60,0:20:53.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.23,0:20:57.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You owe me ten steaks.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.69,0:20:59.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come again?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.87,0:21:01.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You owe me ten steaks.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.61,0:21:07.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, we accept your terms for forgiveness, right, Narukami?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.39,0:21:09.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me too?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.39,0:21:11.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For you, it'll be beef bowls.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.23,0:21:13.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.33,0:21:17.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll forgive you then.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.12,0:21:23.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm completely wiped out.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.45,0:21:24.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Same here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.92,0:21:29.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Konishi and Ms. Yamano were thrown into that dangerous place.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.29,0:21:34.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The people who came in here were attacked by their Shadows,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.25,0:21:37.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}just like Yosuke was a while ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.50,0:21:43.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If someone really did throw them in,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.34,0:21:45.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that's unforgivable.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.11,0:21:47.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll find the culprit and stop him!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.35,0:21:49.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We made a promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.87,0:21:51.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You{\i0} did, anyway.{You did, yeah.}{He says it in a way like "Yeah we ended up making a promise (thanks to you you nigger lol)"}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.85,0:21:53.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.27,0:21:57.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think that, with you, I can find the culprit
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.05,0:21:59.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and solve the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.53,0:22:06.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'll be counting on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.72,0:22:08.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.47,0:22:12.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{ED}
Dialogue: 2,0:22:25.94,0:22:26.86,Copy of ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)\blur2}No time to waste
Dialogue: 2,0:22:26.86,0:22:27.57,Copy of ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(50,50)}but make you pace
Dialogue: 2,0:22:27.57,0:22:29.53,Copy of ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(50,50)}It's okay to remove, copy, and paste
Dialogue: 2,0:22:29.53,0:22:30.41,Copy of ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(50,50)}I'm doing my way
Dialogue: 2,0:22:30.41,0:22:31.28,Copy of ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(50,50)}You do it your way
Dialogue: 2,0:22:31.28,0:22:33.03,Copy of ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(50,50)}Don't just follow your left, find the right way
Dialogue: 2,0:22:33.03,0:22:33.83,Copy of ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(50,50)}Stereotypes
Dialogue: 2,0:22:33.83,0:22:34.74,Copy of ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(50,50)}Too many hypes,
Dialogue: 2,0:22:34.74,0:22:36.45,Copy of ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(50,50)}But I'm the epitome of new types
Dialogue: 2,0:22:36.45,0:22:37.96,Copy of ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(50,50)}Having the fear is power to my soul
Dialogue: 2,0:22:37.96,0:22:39.08,Copy of ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(50,50)}'Cause I overcome them
Dialogue: 2,0:22:39.08,0:22:39.83,Copy of ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(50,50)}That's how I roll
Dialogue: 2,0:22:39.83,0:22:41.50,Copy of ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(50,50)}Expose your thoughts
Dialogue: 2,0:22:41.50,0:22:44.96,Copy of ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(50,50)}Don't be afraid of making mistakes
Dialogue: 2,0:22:44.96,0:22:47.38,Copy of ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(50,50)}Rules prevailing in
Dialogue: 2,0:22:47.92,0:22:52.72,Copy of ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(50,50)}That may be your greatest rival
Dialogue: 2,0:22:53.64,0:22:57.10,Copy of ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(50,50)}Believe in faith and your heart
Dialogue: 2,0:22:57.10,0:23:01.65,Copy of ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(50,50)}Your true soul stop being in the shades
Dialogue: 2,0:23:01.65,0:23:06.28,Copy of ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(50,50)}Come on, out in the open sun
Dialogue: 2,0:23:06.86,0:23:11.99,Copy of ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(50,50)}Beauty of the child of destiny
Dialogue: 2,0:23:13.66,0:23:15.66,Copy of ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(50,50)}Delightful days
Dialogue: 2,0:23:16.04,0:23:20.42,Copy of ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(50,50)}are with rich density of love
Dialogue: 2,0:23:20.83,0:23:22.21,Copy of ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(50,50)}Thorny path
Dialogue: 2,0:23:23.21,0:23:27.55,Copy of ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(50,50)}There's no easy way for real bliss
Dialogue: 2,0:23:27.92,0:23:31.18,Copy of ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(50,50)}So I keep on fighting for
Dialogue: 2,0:23:31.18,0:23:35.47,Copy of ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(50,50)}Beauty of destiny
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{Part C}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.11,0:23:43.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Is it true that you're the manager, even though you're still in high school?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.59,0:23:46.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No, I'm only filling in for my mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.12,0:23:48.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You're looking gorgeous in that kimono!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.84,0:23:50.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Huh? I don't know...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.84,0:23:54.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Is it true that Ms. Yamano stayed at your inn before she died?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.60,0:23:55.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.74,0:23:57.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad's late again.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.62,0:24:01.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I need to do the dishes.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.25,0:24:02.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll help.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.16,0:24:05.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{preview}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.25,0:24:17.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hanamura! Narukami!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.44,0:24:19.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.45,0:24:20.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He bit me.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.29,0:24:21.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good evening!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.59,0:24:23.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? I don't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.75,0:24:24.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See you tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.79,0:24:26.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't come near me!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.70,0:24:27.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't look at me!
